        "readmeExcerpt": "XAgent is an autonomous AI agent from OpenBMB built around a dual-loop architecture: an outer-loop planner that decomposes goals into plans, and inner-loop executors that carry out individual tasks with tools.\n\n### 🎯 Use Cases\n- **Complex Multi-Step Tasks**: Long-horizon goals that exceed single-LLM reasoning.\n- **Tool-Heavy Workflows**: File system, web browser, terminal, and code interpreter.\n- **Research on Agent Design**: Reference implementation of planner/executor patterns.\n\n### ✨ Features\n- Dual-loop planner/executor architecture\n- Built-in tools: web, files, code interpreter\n- Docker-based execution environment\n- Web UI for monitoring agent state\n\n### 👍 Pros\n- Clean separation of planning and execution\n- Strong sandboxing through Docker\n- Useful blueprint for building your own agent\n\n### 👎 Cons & Limitations\n- Less active development than mainstream agent frameworks\n- Heavier setup compared to lightweight alternatives"
